_sText:
This map is a bunch of pools connected at the underside two bridges connecting the starting sides holes to jump down into pools in case of emergency, some guns are littered around the map. A bunch of different ways to play this map, its cool for knife fights as well as normal games. its also got a box in each spawn zone with 3 M421s and 8 grenades.  have fun and dont run by the pool
